Name: Average time from 'Declaration APPROVED by BUDGET OWNER' to 'Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration APPROVED by BUDGET OWNER' and activity 'Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR'

Name: Average time between 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION' and 'Declaration APPROVED by BUDGET OWNER'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION' and activity 'Declaration APPROVED by BUDGET OWNER'

Name: Average resolution time of 'Declaration APPROVED by BUDGET OWNER'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Declaration APPROVED by BUDGET OWNER and the end of the case

Name: Total time from 'Declaration APPROVED by BUDGET OWNER' to 'Payment Handled'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Declaration APPROVED by BUDGET OWNER' and activity 'Payment Handled'

Name: Minimum time from 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE' to 'Declaration APPROVED by BUDGET OWNER'
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Declaration APPROVED by BUDGET OWNER'

Name: Average waiting time to the 'Declaration APPROVED by BUDGET OWNER' after 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION' and activity 'Declaration APPROVED by BUDGET OWNER'

Name: Total resolution time of cases involving 'Declaration APPROVED by BUDGET OWNER' before 'Request Payment'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Declaration APPROVED by BUDGET OWNER' and activity 'Request Payment'

Name: Minimum time it takes 'Declaration APPROVED by BUDGET OWNER' after the execution of 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION'
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION' and activity 'Declaration APPROVED by BUDGET OWNER'

Name: Average time it takes from 'Declaration APPROVED by BUDGET OWNER' to 'Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR' compared to 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION' to 'Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration APPROVED by BUDGET OWNER' and activity 'Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR'

Name: Total time for 'Declaration APPROVED by BUDGET OWNER' in cases where 'Declaration REJECTED by PRE_APPROVER' occurred
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Declaration APPROVED by BUDGET OWNER' and the end of case where activity 'Declaration REJECTED by PRE_APPROVER occurs

Name: Average time for 'Declaration APPROVED by BUDGET OWNER' in successful payment cases
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration APPROVED by BUDGET OWNER' and activity 'Payment Handled'

Name: Minimum resolution time of 'Declaration APPROVED by BUDGET OWNER' in cases exceeding two months duration from trip date
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity Declaration APPROVED by BUDGET OWNER and the end of the case

Name: Average time from 'Declaration APPROVED by BUDGET OWNER' to 'Request Payment' in cases with prior director approval
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration APPROVED by BUDGET OWNER' and activity 'Request Payment'

Name: Total time it takes the 'Declaration APPROVED by BUDGET OWNER' to be done in cases with domestic declarations
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Declaration APPROVED by BUDGET OWNER and the end of the case

Name: Average time to 'Declaration APPROVED by BUDGET OWNER' grouped by 'org:resource' to identify bottlenecks in the approval process
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration APPROVED by BUDGET OWNER' and the end of case grouped by the last value of org:resource
